OL,3,CFamilies' heartbreak as new figures
OL,4,Cshow rise in drugs-related deaths
OL,6,FCaitlin White was like any other 15-
OL,7,Fyear-old girl. She enjoyed spending
OL,8,Ftime with friends and worked hard in
OL,9,Fschool - with a particular love of art.
OL,11,FHowever, in May 2017, everything
OL,12,Fchanged.
OL,14,FIn a woodland in Portadown, Caitlin
OL,15,Ftook an ecstasy pill and collapsed
OL,16,Fwhile there with friends.
OL,18,FShe died in Craigavon Area Hospital a
OL,19,Fshort time later despite attempts to
OL,20,Fsave her.
