OL,3,CFamilies' heartbreak as new figures
OL,4,Cshow rise in drugs-related deaths
OL,6,FHer family is now calling for better
OL,7,Feducation for young people about the
OL,8,Fdangers drugs pose.
OL,10,FSpeaking exclusively to UTV, in her
OL,11,Ffirst TV interview, Caitlin's aunt
OL,12,Fsaid she lives with the memory of
OL,13,Fseeing her niece shortly before she
OL,14,Fdied.
OL,16,FAs Caitlin's family continue to deal
OL,17,Fwith their loss, figures released by
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland Statistics and
OL,19,FResearch Agency show a rise in drug-
OL,20,Frelated deaths over the past decade.
