OL,3,CFamilies' heartbreak as new figures
OL,4,Cshow rise in drugs-related deaths
OL,6,FLast year, 154 people died from a drug-
OL,7,Frelated cause. That marks a 40%
OL,8,Fincrease over the last decade.
OL,10,FMore than half of drug-related deaths
OL,11,Finvolved an opioid such as heroin and
OL,12,Fmorphine.
OL,14,FPressures are now mounting on those
OL,15,Fworking within rehabilitation centres
OL,16,Fas well as those working in primary
OL,17,Fcare as they tackle Northern Ireland's
OL,18,Fdrugs crisis.
